description.value: Fabulous Queen Village corner property!! Located on a quiet tree lined street, this home has been owned, lived in, & cared for by the same family for decades. Newer Rehab!! Everything has been updated. Kitchen with KitchenAid stainless appliance package, cabinets w granite counters, tiled back splash & floors. Huge fully tiled bathroom!! Original hardwood floors totally refinished. Natural gas service provides radiant heat and gas cooking. Great outdoor space off kitchen & private deck on second floor.!!! This is an absolute Must See home!!

description.value: Meticulously maintained by the owner for over four decades, this rare and exceptional free-standing residence, within a quiet gated community, offers a level of privacy seldom found in the city. Distinguished by a meticulously crafted brick half-wall that graces the entire front facade, this property boasts a dedicated secured private parking space and a generously-sized garden spanning the width of the home, creating a true urban oasis. The third-floor sunroom, adorned with a skylight, exposed brick, and expansive arched windows, floods the space with an abundance of natural light. This home offers three bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and the potential for a finished basement. Whether you're ready to move right in or use it as a blank canvas to create the home of your dreams, this property offers endless possibilities. Savor the culinary delights of the neighborhood, from the charming Pizzeria Stella to the iconic Famous 4th St Deli, or elevate your dining experience at the renowned Zahav. Enjoy seamless access to public transportation, the top-rated Meredith School, world-class healthcare facilities, celebrated cultural venues, and a diverse culinary scene. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a unique piece of Queen Village living in Philadelphia.
